         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] Desires (are not permanent) with men</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] who renounces [desires] in order not (to be born) again</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] (one should) not (be troubled) by the mind</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] bit by bit, (every) moment</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] like (a chariot-maker who) [cuts out] from leather</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] If (one searches for) all (happiness)</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
         <div type="comments">
